messages.content: The figures approached a large tree, with five names carved into the base, and a ladder leading up to what seems to be a normal house, it takes a few minutes for them to get up but as soon as they do get up there, they place Hamachi on their couch, “Hello? Are you awake?”

The mun groaned, starting to slowly open her eyes. She sat up, looked around, saw the two muns and went into defense mode. She scrambled off the couch, tail rattling. She was hissing and shaking. She looked terrified

“Wait! It’s ok! Calm-Calm down, please! We’re not going to hurt you..” one of them holds up his hands, though gives her space, “My, name is Nox, and this.” He pauses, pointing to the other mun, “Is my fiancé, Lolite.” Nox slowly explains.

She stared at them for a bit, tail no longer rattling. "A-Ah.....So-Sorry....I......I wasnt sure....if you guys where real...Im Hamichi...." She was still shaking a bit however....and ber head hurt like hell still

“It’s a pleasure to meet, though I wish not with these circumstances, We’re real, promise....please, sit on the couch, you look exhausted..” his closed eyes scrunched in concern, Lolite extended his hand to the shaking girl
She nodded and stood up and sat on the couch. "I-I dont wanna so-sound rude but....I-I dont....wanna be touched ri-right now...." She looked at Lolite.
“Ah, my dearest apologies...” he curtsies, before Nox speaks up again, “Does anything hurt? We saw you unconscious on the road....” he sighs,
"Uh....M-My hand and my head....Though....my head is...probably hurting from memories resurfacing that....I tried to forget....Superbia....cut my hand with a sword...." She showed him her hand

“I see.,,.Love? Get the first aid kit from the cabinet.” “On it!” The mun exits the living room 
“......Do you need anything else? Drink? Food?” He tilts his head

"Uh....Wa-Water would be nice....Th-Thank you...." She had begun to play with her hair, trying to keep her hands busy so she didnt start scratching at herself, something she did when really scared/nervous
“Got it....is there anyone we can contact for you? Do you have a place to stay?”
"Im staying with Sarcio....but....hes sick....I dont know if Nexum is still there though....." She sighed "I....Dont have a phone...Castus broke it...."

“Sarcio? Hmmm I’m afraid I haven’t heard of him maybe I can join a group chat....” he pulls his terrasect, meanwhile Lolite returns with that white box, “**Can you do me a favor and show me the cut?**”
She nodded and showed him her hand. It didnt seem that deep luckily
“**Mhm, doesn’t seem too deep, a small amount of bandage will do it...”** he hummed, pulling out the gauge, “**are you alright with me wrapping it?**”
She nodded "Ye-Yeah..."

“**Alright, just tell me when it hurts too much.**” he starts gently applying a cream to the wound, 
“Damn, no one has responded yet....and this is the only open group chat I can find..” Nox frowns.
She winced a bit but let him continue
After dabbing on the cream, he quickly wraps it up with the gauge “**”aaaanndd There! Pretty great work if I do say so myself~**” he grins
"Thanks..." She smiled a small bit
A sigh of relief leaves Nox, “Thank god, someone’s coming..”
"Wh-wh-" she felt everything tilting "Nonononono- H-Hold onto something! Castus actived his stands power...!"
“Shit! HOLD ON!” He open his eyes, the whites of them intensing as a BURST of wind surrounds the house, keeping it somewhat steady
Hamichi is shaking and her tail is rattling again. Shes _terrified_
“**HAAAAAAAAAA**” Nox yells as the wind intensifies, the nearby trees shaking violently, Lolite holds on to whatever he could
Shes starting to panic and is digging her nails into her arms as tears stream down her face
“H-Hey! Hamachi? Right?! It’s going to be alright, you already survived so much! I promise nothings gonna happen to you!” Lolite calls out
She can hardly hear him. Everything sounds so muffled to her. Shes panicking. She cant deal with this. She knows that if it keeps tilting the world will possibly restart
The tliting stopped, causing Nox to close his eyes and clutch forehead in pain, the wind ceasing, “ow...f-fuck....” he groaned
Hamichi is shaking and digging her nails into her arms. Its enough to draw blood. She hasnt noticed to tilting stopped
“H-Hey! Hamachi! Hamachi! “ Lolite panics, “It’s over! Your fine!” He runs over to her,
She snaps back to reality and stops digging her nails into her skin. "Th-th-thank goodness i-its over....." She sounded so scared
“Ye-Yeah....oh dear you arms...” he mumbles, while Nox collapses onto the couch
"H-Huh?" She looked at her arms, seeing they where bleeding. The cracks where probably still there as well. "Ah...." She then looked over at Nox "Ar-Are you ok...?"
“I’m-Im fine...” he breathes out, “Just really painful to open my eyes...” The unicorn Esk mun rubbed his closed eyes,
She nodded a bit. She wanted to help but had no idea what to do....

Her head still hurt...

There was a knock on the door to the tree house "Its Buneries! Im here to get Hamichi....!" They called out
“C-Come....in..” Nox weakly responded.

Buneries came in fully and dusted themselves off. 

Hamichi had just....kinda retreated into her mindscape for now
Hamichi snapped back to reality with a small jolt.
“Oh, Hamachi....someone’s.....here for you...” he mumbled.
"....Is...it ok if....I stay until Im sure you're ok......?" She asked, rubbing her arm a bit
“Hmmm? You really don’t need to......but...I’m sure that be fine...”
"Its just.....you....so kindly helped me when....you didnt even know who I am....I just.....wanna repay the favor somehow......." She hummed
".....God this is all my fault.....If I hadnt gotten my memories stolen Sarcio wouldn't be dying...." She mumbled quietly, honestly hoping no one would hear that

".....Im.....gonna head back to Sarcios house....Nox thank you for helping me....." She stood up and went to leave but.....really didnt get far....she had stood up from the couch a little too quickly and that mixed with how sleep deprived she was made her pass out

Buneries quickly caught her "Oh geez....."
Nox, jolted up, “AH! Is....” he clutches his head harder as he felt it throb in pain, “Is...She ok?”
Buneries looked her over before noticing the dark bags under her eyes "I think shes just....really tired....How long has it been since she slept....."
“I....I’m not sure....we found her unconscious on the streets....who knows.....how long she’s been there...”

"Thats worrying....." Their tail swished a bit "......I hate to ask you of this but....Is....it ok if I leave her here for now? I think its best if she is with someone incase something happens.....I have to talk to Dominus about something and Im worried about her....."

“Mhm...it’s really nothing....I’m sure we can manage...” he smiles, “We have a spare room for when Anguis stays over that Hamachi can sleep in...” Nox stretches, slowly standing up. The throbbing starting to cease
They nodded "I can carry her to there...." They stand up "Ah- I dont think I officially introduced myself....Im Buneries but please, call me Bun..."
“I see, it’s very nice to meet you Bun...” he’s somehow able to walk towards Buneries even though his eyes are closed, and holds his hand out to shake.
Buneries smiled a bit and shook his hand
“So, If you don’t mind telling me.....how long might she need to stay here?” He tilts his head

"Hopefully not long. Im gonna watch over her and Sarcio after all the kid muns are able to move into Dominus' temple to stay safe and far from any fights going on during the revolution..." they hummed
“I see....well I promise my and Lolite will do our best to care for her.” He nods, yawning, himself.
"Thank you...I appreciate it....Is there anything you want or anything I can do in return to repay this favor?"
“I really don’t need much....though If possible.....could you look out for a blue tiger stripped mun.....and one with white feathery wings.....just...tell me if you see them and where.”
"Oh! Ive already seen the blue tiger stripped mun! Veteris is at Dominus' temple!" They hummed  "However I havent seen the one with wings yet but Ill keep an eye out."
A small gasp escapes ..”So.....he *is* alive...” he quietly mumbles under his breath. “Thank you....”
They nodded "Do you want me to tell him you where looking for him??"
“No, that won’t be necessary....” he quickly waves the concern off,
"Alright..." They hummed, still holding Hamichi
“I suppose she should get to bed....poor girl seems shaken to the bone..” he sighs, looked concerned at the sleeping Hamachi
"Yeah....From what I remember.....She....went through alot as a human....I feel bad for her...."
(Nya
“A lot as a human?.....I can....relate to that...”
"I dont wanna speak for her...I think its good if she tells you if she wants and.....Im....aware of what you went through....and god...I wish you didn't have to..." They sighed

“I see....well...o don’t blame you for it...She doesn’t have to tell me...” he looks back up
“I’ll prepare the bedroom....”
Buneries shifts Hamichi so shes more comfortable "Alright.."
Hamichi is shaking a bit...Buneries noticed and tries to use their power to help calm her
“Oh....” he look down at the shaking girl....unsure of what to do or if he should touch her.
Hamichis eyes shoot open and she falls out of Buneries arms. Shes half awake but doesnt wanna fall back asleep...
“**Ah! Are you ok**?” He tried to catch her in a way she wouldn’t hit her head.
"I-Im....fine.." She rubbed her eyes  before trying to stand up
She was most definitely not fine...evident by just how tired she looked
Nox frowned, and his Brow furrowed, “Hamachi, come with me.”
She tilted her head "Alright...." She stood up, albeit a bit wobbly due to how tired she was

His footsteps echoed through the halls as he entered presumably his/Lolites room, 
Nox remained silent as he opened a Closet, shifting through the hanged clothes until the mun finally pulls out an old box.
She tilted her head again, not sure what to say.
He opened it, and while searching for something he nonchalantly asks, “Hamachi.....do you have trouble sleeping? Please.....answer honestly...”
"....Yeah....I do....I....have alot of monsters in my mindscape and...they terrify me...." She sighed

“I se......aha! Found..it” he pulls something out, that’s hard to see at first, but as he turns around it’s clear that it’s a handmade Ram plush, though it’s age shows, and whoever made used too much fuzz for wool, for its  hard to see its legs. A doll sized cowbell is tied tightly around it’s neck with a red ribbon.
She stared at it "It....looks really cute...." Why was he showing it to her though? Thats what she was confused by

“Heh...My Nanna made it.....they are really cute....I remember she called them....Contego....” he gave a small smile, “This lil fella always made me feel safe.....And....I’m Wondering....if you’d like them.”
She stared. He...was willing to give it to her....? She was a mun he hardly knew.....Yet he was being so kind "....Y-Yes....I....I would..."
He outstretched his hands to her, Contego’s bell jingling with the movement
She gently took it and held it close to her, tail wagging a small bit
It felt, extremely soft and warm, with its constant sleeping expression, the bells jingles again.
She began to purr a bit before yawning "Soft....."
She was struggling to keep her eyes open....
“Here....you should rest..,I’ll sleep on the couch,” he patted the beds mattress
"Are... you sure....? This is your house....." She mumbled, yawning a bit
“Positive.” He gives a reassuring smile and nods
She nodded and laid down on the bed, falling asleep almost instantly
He strides over and covers her up with the blanket, turning off the light as he closed the door and left. Sighing
After a while Hamichi wakes up, not with a start. She...was actually able to get some rest. "I....feel well rested....I-I....actually got some sleep....!" She smiled. She had to thank Nox.
The smell of batter wafts from outside the door
Her tail wagged a bit at that as she went to go find Nox "Nox....?" She called out

Nox was sitting at the kitchen table, sipping a cup of tea, Lolite humming as he flipped the source of the delectable smell, Hamachi’s footsteps alerted them both, Nox giving a gentle smile, “Ah, Hamachi.....you’re finally awake...” the other Mun chimed in with a sing songy voice, “We made pancakes!~~”
She smiled at that "I was actually able to get some sleep.....I...feel pretty good. And pancakes sound good.....I cant remember the last time I had them..." Her tail was wagging a bit more
A chuckle left Nox “Lolite picked up too much batter from the grocery store yesterday....I hope you have an appetite...”

"Well....I certainly think I do...I....dont remember when I ate last. I...kinda have trouble knowing when to eat and stuff....I....was rasied in a cult who saw me as their god. They....didnt let me do anything for myself so.....Its kinda messed me up. But! Im no longer there and im trying to work on getting better." She played with her hair a bit. She felt comfortable enough around these 2 muns to reveal that

The energy in the room turned solemn, “Oh..,....well.. I’m very happy...that you got out...” the horned mun spoke, taking another sip of his tea, *was Dios following considered a cult? He might need to research later.....*
She noticed the shift in energy "Ah- Im sorry.....I-I didnt mean to make you guys sad......" She rubbed her arm a bit, looking away. Had she messed up? Should she of held her tounge?
“No! Please...do not apologize....we’re just...surprised you felt comfortable enough with us to share.” He tried to lighten the mood with another smile
She looked at them again "Ah- Yeah I just....Feel comfortable around you guys....Its....Its a nice feeling....to actually feel comfortable y'know?" She smiled a small bit
“Mhm...that’s nice..” a plate slides towards Hamachi ag the table, a few pancakes stacked on eachother, drizzled with syrup, Lolite giving a wink
Hamichi seemed excited, tail starting to wag. She digs in, her tail wagging more. Shes practically in heaven from how good it tastes
....Is she tearing up???? She is.
This earns a confident laugh from the cook, “HA HA! I KNEW IT! I **AM** THE BETTER COOK!” He strikes a pose, which Nox snorts to, trying not to spit out the tea, “*oh my god loli*”
She swallows and speaks "Its _good_. God I can't remember the last time I've had food that tastes this good!!!!" She giggled
“Hehehe well I am the *best-*”
She giggled again, a happy smile on her face. Her tail was wagging quite a bit
“*Someone at least likes my cooking dear~*”  he gives a fake betrayed look to Nox who laughs and shakes his head, “Lol, I love you...but you can be too much..”
She continues to eat the pancakes she has infront of her happily
“**And you can be a bitter anime character at times yet I’m still here~**” the purple mun jokingly chastised with a sway of his hips, this time, causing Nox to choke on his drink
Her raised an eyebrow at them but continued to eat. Shes....basically scarfing it down...She really should slow down
After coughing for a few seconds, Nox turns to Hamachi, “Hey, Don’t eat them too fast, you’ll get a stomachache...”
She nodded and slowed down on her eating of the pancakes.
Soon enough she had finished....andddd she had the hiccups now.
“Pfft I told you,” he chuckled
She stuck her tounge out, giggling a bit
“Why you-“ Nox reached over and tried to ruffle her hair, Lolite now sitting at the table with his own plate of pancakes, very amused at the situation.
She giggled more, tail wagging. She just seemed really relaxed

“*Hmm, I’m....not too sure what to do today....*” he sighed taking another sip, “Well....there’s some parts of the house that need repair after the world tilt thingy...” Lolite spoke up through bites of pancake.
"I can help you guys if you want...! " she just wants to feel useful. But ..theres a voice in the back on her mind telling her to not get attached otherwise they'll end up hurt as well because of her
“That be great, Hamachi.” Nox turned his head, to her, “I also think we can chip up the paint as well.”
Her tail wagged and she smiled. Horray she would actually be useful for a bit!
"I can start while you guys finish eating....!" She suggested
“I suggest we all should do it.” The stardust haired one spoke up, “More fun that way..”
She nodded "Ok!!! Thats a good idea.." She hummed
She had a plan in store for later. She knew it would help. It had to help.
“Why don’t we start right now? We’ll get things done before sundown then.” Nox finished his tea and placed the cup on the kitchen counter, standing up.
Hamichi stood up as well "Ok! Sounds good." She smiled
“Let’s do the outside first then!” He started walking towards the door, Lolite shoving one more bite of pancake into his mouth before following
Hamichi followed after as wel, humming q bit
When they got outside there were already buckets of paint next to the ladder, “hmm should we take sections?”
"Sounds like a good idea. We can get it done faster that way!" She took a bucket with her tail, seeing if she could lift it
It was pretty light! Seems like thin paint, the other two take their buckets and brushes, Lolite climbing up the huge tree to start painting the walls, Nox straying around the base of it
Hamichi went to a spot that was kinda hidden to start painting
After a while, she makes sure no one can see her before sneaking off. It was now or never for her....

Neither of them noticed 
For now
She went into a more heavily wooded section and began to set up the ritual to summon the spirits again. She was chanting as well

It took a bit for Nox to notice Hamachi’s disappearance 
“.....Lolite stay here..”
Shes almost done with the ritual. She just needs to active it with her blood. She has no knife....but she has her fangs and horns....
He ran into woods, searching frantically for Hamachi, panic setting in, “**HA.....HAMACHI**”
She felt bad hearing his panicked voice. But she had to finish. She bit into her hand, making sure to draw enough blood and held it over the ritual circle
“**HAMACHI**” his voice became louder as he came into view, rushing towards her, one of his eyes slightly peeked open, a small breeze coming with him
The circle began to glow. She hadn't expected him to find her....She...felt even worse now
“**HAMA GET AWAY FROM THAT!!!**” he yells, shoving Hamachi out of the circle, Nox had no clue what that.....circle was.....but he hated the feeling it gave him....

Her eyes widened "DONT STAND IN IT!" She didn't want them to possess him...She was supposed to be the host! 

Nox could feel a sudden tug on his mind
Nox clutched his head.....the tugging felt familiar...in a horrible way....he vould almost hallucinate those retched golden strings appearing on his wrists,  his breaths quicken

"Nonononono- N-Nox you have to fight them off...!" She was terrified

He could hear voices, the main one sounded.....motherly....almost caring in tone...
“...what...do I do.....? What do I do....?” Noxs voice is shaky His leg quake and tail drooping, “the voices........scare me....”

"D-Dont let them take control!" She was desperately trying to remember the exorcism that had been performed on her years ago to free her....

'_Give in dear.....It will all be ok....We can help you..._' The voices said

“They sound so.....nice.....it scares me......” 
a small part of him....wanted to listen to them though.....they sound so comforting....something that he needed.

She was panicking greatly now "Pl-Please! Dont give in!"

'_Everything will all be ok....just give in....you can trust us....We only want to help~_'
“I-I’m so tired Hama.....they’re too loud....” he whimpered, rubbing his eyes, he’s started to stumble around.

Shes tearing up, still desperately trying to remember the exorcism.

'_Just let yourself fall asleep....Dont worry about a thing.....~_'

He felt his conscious slowly slip away
“I’m.....I’m...sorry....Ham....ma.” Nox mumbled, slouched over

She felt tears start to fall "Fuck- L-Leave his body! Arent I the one you want?!"

The spirits took over with a laugh
His movements became more puppet like and jolty as he straightens up, His laugh blending with the spirits
"I-I said leave his body!" She was so scared as she began to back up a bit
His head tilts, “hmmm strange vision....no color excepts black, white.....grey...” he seemed to ignore Hamachi’s pleading
"Mother _Please!_ Get out of him! Arent I the host you want?!" She whimpered
Another laugh escapes, “Oh...Oh my little Hamachi......We don’t need you anymore...this.,*this new body is just...*” his limbs jankily trace against his skin, “**too exquisite..**”
"Then.....T-Then Ill make you get out!!!" Her voice was shakey. She was terrified. She had to remember the exorcism.
“Really?” He took a step towards Hamachi, “Hit me with your best shot then Hamachi....” he took another
She had frozen in fear. She couldnt move. She didnt want to hurt him....

The possessed mun was ready to strangle Hamachi but a whistled tune  is heard, and soon enough a slash cut appeared on his cheek, causing him to hiss and back away...”Who.....”
“**Get out of my boyfriend you paranormal Bitch**”
Hamichi had teared up "L-Lolite...! I-Im sorry- T-This is all m-my fault-" She whimpered
"I-I thought summoning them and be-being their host again would make m-me more useful b-but they t-took over N-Nox...."
He hops down from the branch he was on“....We can have that talk later....right now we have to deal with....this..” he turns to Nox now recovering from the shock, “do you have an idea?”
"I-I need to perform an exorcism...B-But I cant remember it...." She whimpered "I-Im trying but i can only remember bits and pieces...."
“Well...uh....Well then....recite those pieces! Even if it’s not the whole thing it’s bound to do something!!!”
She nodded and began to do so. Her voice was shakey but she had to do thism

The possessed Nox yells in pain, covering his hears, “shut up shut up shut up”
Eyes started appearing on his arms and neck. He charges at Lolite, intending to stab him with his horn, the other using Death by Glamour to keep him at arms length, “come on Hamachi.....”
She starts to remember more as she recites the exorcism. Shes starting to feel more confident as her voice gets less shakey and more loud
(Nya
His yells start to cease as he slowly looks up, “Hama....chi?” Even though his eyes are closed, fear can be seen on his face,
She smiled at him before getting to the end of the exorcism. She had to finish it. Just to be safe.
"....Are.....You ok Nox....?" She asked, a worried look on her face

Collapsing on his knees, Nox frantically, almost tearing them, pulls his fuzzy gloves off, checking his wrist while clutching it tightly, the tattoos obscuring the stitches......no golden string......that’s good....but it didn’t do much to calm him down, his breathes stuttering, “H......”
She rubbed her arm a bit. God she really had messed up...."I-Im sorry......"
“It....it’s ok....it’s....I’m..Ok....” Nox mumbles as Lolite crouches next to his lover, holding him close, “Hamichi, I know you didn’t mean harm but....what the hell just happened...?”

"....You.....remember how I said I was raised in a cult...? Well....I was a host to 3 spirits.....Its why I was worshipped....I....thought if I was their host again they would help me.....I....I dont know how to do much on my own...." She sniffled a bit, trying to not cry "B-But my hope....was well....shortlived.....They dont care...Th-They never did......" She was starting to dig her nails into her arms again.... "Im stupid! Im so stupid for thinking they would help! Everything is my fault!"
Nox, shifted out of Lolites grip, and tugged on Hamichi jacket, “Come here.....”
She whimpered a bit and got closer to him, starting to cry more
She couldn't hold it in anymore and just began to sob
He softly hugged her, “it’s.....alright....you can cry now...”
She just kept sobbing, finally letting herself actually cry
She keeps crying until she just...cant anymore
“Shhhh.....just breathe...” Nox whispered....taking his own advice ad well
"I-I cant....remember the last time I cried like that...." She sniffled, wiping her eyes
“Well...now You let it all out....that’s good.”
".....Th-Thank you....both of you.....fo-for being so kind....."

"Oh...I....know something that...can actually be useful....protection spells.....keeps spirits away...." She hummed "I can draw a few up if you guys want....." She had taken her coat off to try and stop her arms from bleeding from when she dug her nails in. Her cracked arms where out for the 2 to see. 'I gotta work on fixing the cracks......' she thought to herself
“......We need to take care of your arms first..” he interrupts, concerned when seeing the cuts,
She nodded a bit "Gotta....Make sure the summoning circle can't be used anymore first...." She used her hands to disrupt it "There.....Destroyed...."
She tied her jacket around her waist as she turned back to the 2
“Here,” Nox turns around at pats his back, “If I carry you we can travel faster.”
She nodded a bit and got on his back
“**Lets get outta here before the Wolves arrive!”** Lolite said with a flick of his hat, as he booked it, Nox, Hamichi on his back, follows suit, though at a slower pace.
Wolves. Something Hamichi never wanted to encounter again. Not after she was attacked and nearly killed by one.
"Don't like wolves.....especially after one nearly killed me.....Nexum and Duvet saved me..." She mumbled
“Yeah....there’s a especially hostile pack around here, the Leader mostly.......” Lolite shrugged, “Whos Nexum and Duvet though?”
"Nexum is a....friend. Yeah Im pretty sure we are friends....Duvet is her stand!" She hummed "Giant robot bird thing.....very nice....."
“Oh! Maybe someday we can meet them...” Nox smiles
"A fair warning, Nexum....can be pretty odd at times. More like all the time." She chuckled "But shes cool....I hope shes doing ok...."
“I date Lolite....I’m sure I could handle it..” he chuckled, though a fake gasp overpowers it “**How DARE**”
Hamichi giggled, tail wagging a bit. She was starting to feel a bit better.....her cracks lessened a bit....
The trip was going smoothly, only passing a few wolves even then they were sleeping
She stared at the wolves sleeping. Scary still to her....
She yawned a bit, staring to feel tired
"....I....just realized....Nexum probably has no idea where I am......Uh....Could....I borrow someone's Tesseract to let her know im ok...?"
“Hmm? You can borrow mine.” Nox answered as they arrived at the base,
"Thank you..." She smiled a bit
"Hmm....Later maybe I can show off my acrobatic skills for you guys!!" She hummed
His smile brightened as he pulled out the tesseract, holding it out to her, “I can’t wait.”
Her tail began to wag at that and she took the Tesseract

Lolite took a glance at a conversation before growling diverted his attention, “*Oh* **SHIT**, uh, maybe you can talk more oncewegetinthe**HOUSE**-“ his voice cracked and he started to climb the ladder
Nox followed suit Hamichi on his back, as a group of wolves started to approach, the leader wearing a bandanna on its neck,
Hamichi froze up at that, tail starting to rattle to try and scare them off

Eventually they were able to safely get on high ground, Lolite looking down and shouting at the pack
“**OI ZEPYHR, FUCK OFF YOU FURRY BASTARD!!!**” he shakes his fist at them, Nox just sighs, embarrassed
Hamichi snickered a bit at that "Wait- He has a name????"
“No, that’s just what we named him...” he chuckled, “He’s fairly larger then the rest, also longer horns.” “We usually just throw them leftovers and he leaves.”
"Huh....Interesting..." She hummed
"Nexum says its a nice name"
“Yeah, Lolite thinks he’s a stand user but.....I haven’t seen any unusual abilities..” Lolite looks back up, “He just has that aura about him!” He huffed

"Hm...Maybe..." She knows she has a stand....She tries to summon it and it works. "Maybe If....I send my stand down we can see if he sees her...." Shes avoiding looking at her stand....she really doesnt like it

Nox looked intrigued at her stand, “Interesting...” he mumbled, 
Zephyr at the sight of it growls, incensed. Fur fluffed up

"....He....can see it." She was suprised. 

Her stand tilted its head and showed off its sharp teeth, all its eyes staring at Zephyr

“Oh.....that’s....concerning...” 
the wolf tried to batt at it, his ears twitching

The stand stepped back, tilting her head

"Yeah...." She hummed
“What...should we do..?” He asked, Zephyr taking a step forward, barring his own set of teeth.

"I...have no idea." She frowned a bit "I...Dont wanna provoke him more though..."

The stands many eyes kept staring at him before Hamichi willed it away
"....I dont think....I like my stand.....Reminds me of...._her_...." She refused to say her name
Her cracks where glowing a bit. She didnt like thinking of Mother....
“I see....some stands can be frightening, but....they’re truly there to protect you..” he looks to her, with a sympathetic expression
She sighed "I know....I just....wish it didnt have so many eyes....."
"Anyway....Uh....I need...my cuts patches up...." She....really has no idea how to treat wounds that well...

“Right, Lolite, keep an eye on Zephy ok?” His lover nods, “*already on it.*” 
“Hamichi, lets get your cuts patched inside,”
She nodded "Alright...." She hummed a small bit, glancing back down at the wolf pack
(Nya
He opens the sliding door, and gestures for Hamichi to come inside.
She climbed inside, glancing back down. She wanted to be sure Lolite was ok....He was her friend after all...
